                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="benefit-item">
                <div class="border">
                    <h1>2.</h1>
                    <h2>Types of Personal Information Collected</h2>
                    <p>Information we may collect includes, but is not limited to:</p>
                    <ul style="font-size: 1rem;font-family: Gilroy, sans-serif;">
                        <li>Name, ID number, address, phone number, email address</li>
